Green Apple Solutions is an innovative technology focused firm. We have a well balanced portfolio of Social Media services, and technology based solutions.

<h3>Digital</h3>

Our core strength is to help companies manage their digital marketing strategy and investments in social media based on measurable outcomes and in the context of broader, multichannel marketing efforts. We enable marketers to measure their social media efforts, and understand how conversations on social networks and online communities influence marketing performance. Our social media experts help removing the guesswork associated with social media engagement, and replace it with strategies and experimentation built on insight.

<h3>Technology</h3>

At Green Apple Solutions, we use state of the art technology along with our in-depth understanding of business processes to deliver customized solutions and applications. We develop integrated, interoperable and fully scalable business solutions and web applications that function in complex distributed environments. We work with heterogeneous platforms to develop and deliver technology solutions that evolve with business growth and require minimum support.";s:10:"post_title";s:8:"About Us";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:5:"about";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2013-07-29 22:20:35";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2013-07-29 22:20:35";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:35:"http://beta.gas.ind.in/?page_id=509";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:1;O:7:"WP_Post":24:{s:2:"ID";i:529;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"2";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2013-07-31 22:58:02";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2013-07-31 22:58:02";s:12:"post_content";s:1233:"The world is going mobile. With the onset of affordable hardware and the availability of the open source Android more and more people are now using smart phones and using them to access the internet. At this rate of adoption there will soon be a time where a considerable chunk of interaction between corporates and consumers will take place via mobile. This means having an internet strategy, albeit a good one is not enough.  Corporates and Sellers now need to have a mobile strategy so that they now do not lose out on the consumers that wish to connect with them using mobiles.

At Green Apple Solutions we understand the importance of mobile strategy and the value of strategic execution. Our technology experts will understand your requirement and will design, develop and deliver the perfect android application for your business/product that will not only be superior in functionality but also will seamless connect with your existing internet and functional strategies. We will make sure that every consumer who wishes to consume your product or service on his android smart phone will be able to do so is in the most simple and efficient way. Our products are compatible with all flavors of android and all hardware makes.";s:10:"post_title";s:19:"Android Development";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:19:"android-development";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2013-07-31 22:58:02";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2013-07-31 22:58:02";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:499;s:4:"guid";s:35:"http://beta.gas.ind.in/?page_id=529";s:10:"menu_order";i:5;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:2;O:7:"WP_Post":24:{s:2:"ID";i:581;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"2";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2013-07-31 23:29:57";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2013-07-31 23:29:57";s:12:"post_content";s:1901:"Web presence for businesses is no longer optional. No matter how big or small your business is or how wide or narrow your reach is, web presence of your business is a must. In this day and age your website is most of the times the first avenue where your prospective consumers, peers and everyone else interacts with you. You website, its design and its content represent your business and form the first impression of your business on the minds of the visitor.

We at Green Apple Solutions understand the criticality and importance of an appropriate web presence and we realize that your website has to be a representation of your business, its processes, work culture and ethics. We understand that a “one size fits all” website is not going to cut it for you and are committed to provide you with the best website your business deserves. Our design experts go through a phase of thorough research and in-depth understanding of your business, its practices, its vision and culture. This knowledge is then brought to the drawing board along with your requirements and their extensive experience of building highly-usable websites and a custom one-of-a-kind design is created which is unique for you. Our experts use the best tools and technologies that are the best fit for the requirement to provide you with an end product which is not only aesthetically pleasing but also provides a great user experience and is highly functional. We realize the importance of social media in this day and age and ensure that your website is compatible as well as optimized for all the major social platforms. In addition to that we make sure that your website is search engine friendly as well as optimized for mobile viewers. We have extremely high regards for superior user experience and we want your consumer to have the best experience of the website, independent of the medium from which it is consumed.";s:10:"post_title";s:23:"Bespoke Website Designs";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:23:"bespoke-website-designs";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2013-07-31 23:29:57";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2013-07-31 23:29:57";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:483;s:4:"guid";s:35:"http://beta.gas.ind.in/?page_id=581";s:10:"menu_order";i:1;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"po