ction between corporates and consumers will take place via mobile. This means having an internet strategy, albeit a good one is not enough.  Corporates and Sellers now need to have a mobile strategy so that they now do not lose out on the consumers that wish to connect with them using mobiles. At Green Apple Solutions we understand the importance of mobile strategy and the value of strategic execution. We feel that a digital marketing complete cannot be effectively executed if mobile marketing is not a crucial part of the same. We believe in a uniformity of communication and treatment over platforms and make sure that you not only have a definite mobile marketing strategy but also that it is in sync with your other marketing strategies. We use our superior technical prowess to build apps, mobile optimized advertisements and landing pages and mobile friendly websites. Our mobile marketing  experts believe in the sanctity of design and effectiveness of function and make sure that your consumers get the same level of satisfactions when consuming your message from mobile as well as the conventional platforms.

Mobile is the way to go and with Green Apple Solutions you will always stay ahead.";s:10:"post_title";s:17:"Mobile Marketing	";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:16:"mobile-marketing";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2013-07-31 23:27:43";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2013-07-31 23:27:43";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:483;s:4:"guid";s:35:"http://beta.gas.ind.in/?page_id=575";s:10:"menu_order";i:14;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:19;O:7:"WP_Post":24:{s:2:"ID";i:511;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"2";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2013-07-29 22:27:43";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2013-07-29 22:27:43";s:12:"post_content";s:2888:"<h3>Akhil Gupta</h3>
Akhil is an example of a social media "guru," a word the dictionary defines as an "influential expert," in a field that's evolving very rapidly. A Green Apple Solutions stalwart and a social media enthusiast he likes to make smart and shiny things.

Akhil has been a specialist to help marketers directly measure their social media efforts, and understand how social networks influence marketing performance. He helps removing the guesswork from digital and replaces it with strategies and experimentation built on solid insight. He has helped many companies execute their digital campaigns based on measurable outcomes in the context of broader, multichannel marketing efforts.

Additionally, he heads the HR division at Green Apple Solutions.

In the past, Akhil has worked with hedge funds and trading desks in the US as a consultant and helped some of the top Indian companies with their digital marketing campaigns.

He can be contacted at akhil@greenapplesolutions.com

<hr />

<h3>Lakshdeep Rajput</h3>
